<%!--
  One catalog course (F6.5-D8). Renders @course (= Portal.get_course!/1) — the escaped
  title and an :if published badge — purely from the assign. Required so the index
  link ~p"/courses/#{id}" and the create redirect compile under Verified Routes. No
  Repo or context call appears (F6.5-INV1); the title is HEEx-escaped (F6.5-INV2).
--%>
<h1 data-course-title>{@course.title}</h1>
<span :if={@course.published} data-published-badge>Published</span>
